00:00:33,330 --> 00:00:36,580
♪Flowers falling by the river again♪

2
00:00:36,580 --> 00:00:38,840
♪Turning the clear waves red♪

3
00:00:39,820 --> 00:00:44,600
♪Sparrows singing in celebration♪

4
00:00:46,290 --> 00:00:49,530
♪Calm years pass by the silent bustling city♪

5
00:00:49,530 --> 00:00:52,070
♪Sitting at home♪

6
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:58,260
♪No one knows love's outline like I do♪

7
00:00:58,550 --> 00:01:04,640
♪If one day the river breeze blows again♪

8
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:10,980
♪I won't be a mere reflection in the mirror♪

9
00:01:11,470 --> 00:01:17,540
♪Dreams can shatter; Memories remain♪

10
00:01:17,980 --> 00:01:21,230
♪Rich fragrance aids; Light ink writes♪

11
00:01:21,230 --> 00:01:28,090
♪In the deep red windows lies mundane dust♪

12
00:01:33,260 --> 00:01:40,980
=Are You The One=

13
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:43,980
=Episode 7=

14
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:48,100
We did it!

15
00:01:48,360 --> 00:01:49,890
We finally get the dragonfly pattern.

16
00:01:50,440 --> 00:01:51,890
Good heavens.

17
00:01:52,270 --> 00:01:53,780
I've been working for over ten years.

18
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:56,240
These plates are the hardest
I've ever fired.

19
00:01:56,240 --> 00:01:57,440
Let's head to the trade guild now

20
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:58,580
and show them what we've achieved.

21
00:01:59,830 --> 00:02:00,670
Let's go.

22
00:02:01,700 --> 00:02:04,260
(Lingquan Town Porcelain Trade Guild)

23
00:02:04,270 --> 00:02:05,110
Stop right there!

24
00:02:06,030 --> 00:02:07,160
Please announce my arrival.

25
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:08,360
I need to see Young Mr. He.

26
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,810
The Young Mr. He said

27
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:11,290
he's ill

28
00:02:11,430 --> 00:02:12,340
and isn't

29
00:02:12,550 --> 00:02:14,380
seeing anyone, especially women.

30
00:02:19,430 --> 00:02:20,290
My Lord,

31
00:02:20,590 --> 00:02:22,500
the porcelain trade guild
has submitted a joint report,

32
00:02:22,710 --> 00:02:24,660
accusing the Yushao Porcelain Shop in Lingquan

33
00:02:24,660 --> 00:02:25,640
of illegal land acquisition.

34
00:02:28,990 --> 00:02:29,830
Who?

35
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:32,810
Yushao Porcelain Shop
from the porcelain trade guild.

36
00:02:33,390 --> 00:02:34,240
The trade guild

37
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,920
has been monopolizing

38
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:37,290
the porcelain business for years.

39
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:39,780
Ms. Liu only bought a piece of land.

40
00:02:40,040 --> 00:02:41,660
It can't be considered
illegal land acquisition.

41
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:44,040
I must take this opportunity

42
00:02:44,040 --> 00:02:45,410
to teach the trade guild a lesson.

43
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:53,220
B-But

44
00:02:53,670 --> 00:02:55,000
the porcelain business

45
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,320
accounts for a third of

46
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:57,780
Lingquan Town's tax revenue.

47
00:02:58,390 --> 00:03:00,390
Besides, the date for the royal tribute

48
00:03:00,390 --> 00:03:01,570
is just around the corner.

49
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:04,530
Ms. Liu dared to do that.

50
00:03:04,990 --> 00:03:06,290
She should be the one

51
00:03:07,760 --> 00:03:08,600
to be punished.

52
00:03:09,110 --> 00:03:11,060
Ms. Liu purchased the land legally.

53
00:03:11,830 --> 00:03:13,060
What crime is there?

54
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,200
Sorry...

55
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,940
I made a mistake.

56
00:03:21,390 --> 00:03:24,810
How should we handle this case?

57
00:03:25,270 --> 00:03:26,570
I await your instructions,

58
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:28,340
My Lord.

59
00:03:29,920 --> 00:03:30,920
I've already

60
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:31,970
cut their taxes

61
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:34,000
to support their road expansions.

62
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,520
The routes they choose

63
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:37,040
are totally up to them,

64
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:37,940
and Zhenzhou authority

65
00:03:38,270 --> 00:03:39,290
shall not interfere.

66
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:41,010
Yes,

67
00:03:41,590 --> 00:03:42,690
My Lord.

68
00:03:51,990 --> 00:03:52,970
What are you thinking?

69
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:57,010
Honey,

70
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,000
I was turned away

71
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,010
by the He family today.

72
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:02,130
Then I asked around and found out

73
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:03,760
they accused me of illegal land acquisition

74
00:04:03,760 --> 00:04:04,850
to His Lordship.

75
00:04:06,670 --> 00:04:08,100
I heard about that.

76
00:04:10,430 --> 00:04:11,290
That's not your fault.

77
00:04:12,200 --> 00:04:13,150
Even if this issue

78
00:04:13,150 --> 00:04:14,430
reaches Lord Huaiyang,

79
00:04:14,430 --> 00:04:15,460
you still have a valid case.

80
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:17,080
But those merchants

81
00:04:17,080 --> 00:04:18,730
have held power in Lingquan for a long time.

82
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,260
I'm afraid Lord Huaiyang

83
00:04:20,440 --> 00:04:21,970
will listen to them.

84
00:04:22,390 --> 00:04:23,230
No, he won't.

85
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:25,950
From what I know

86
00:04:25,950 --> 00:04:27,220
of Lord Huaiyang,

87
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:29,410
he will uphold justice

88
00:04:29,590 --> 00:04:30,930
and remain unbiased.

89
00:04:34,150 --> 00:04:35,220
Right.

90
00:04:36,030 --> 00:04:37,260
How did I not think of that?

91
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:39,000
Do you trust him now?

92
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:39,840
No.

93
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:41,490
I trust you, honey.

94
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,900
We can't take a hit and stay quiet.

95
00:04:44,080 --> 00:04:44,960
Let's go

96
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:46,630
meet Lord Huaiyang and petition him

97
00:04:46,630 --> 00:04:47,900
to clear this up.

98
00:04:50,350 --> 00:04:51,190
Honey?

99
00:04:54,520 --> 00:04:55,820
Lord Huaiyang is very busy.

100
00:04:56,030 --> 00:04:57,730
That's why you must help.

101
00:04:58,000 --> 00:04:59,120
You play Go with His Lordship,

102
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:00,170
so you can introduce me to him.

103
00:05:00,830 --> 00:05:02,370
- I...
- Nanny Li.

104
00:05:03,470 --> 00:05:05,230
Prepare a formal outfit for me.

105
00:05:05,230 --> 00:05:07,370
We'll go to the Mansion of Lord Huaiyang
this afternoon.

106
00:05:18,820 --> 00:05:20,860
(Cui Mansion)

107
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:21,990
To the Mansion of Lord Huaiyang.

108
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:24,020
Drive steadily.

109
00:05:24,230 --> 00:05:25,070
Yes.

110
00:05:27,740 --> 00:05:31,380
(Cui Mansion)

111
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,220
What a disaster.

112
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:52,520
Honey.

113
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:54,520
When we meet His Lordship,

114
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:55,780
follow my lead.

115
00:05:56,590 --> 00:05:57,430
Follow your lead?

116
00:05:58,520 --> 00:05:59,470
Well,

117
00:05:59,470 --> 00:06:00,510
all you need to do

118
00:06:00,510 --> 00:06:01,610
is build a good rapport with him.

119
00:06:01,960 --> 00:06:04,020
I'll handle the business.

120
00:06:04,150 --> 00:06:05,140
You won't need to say anything.

121
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:06,780
Don't be so nervous.

122
00:06:11,960 --> 00:06:13,470
His Lordship and Ms. Liu will arrive soon.

123
00:06:13,470 --> 00:06:14,560
You'll pose as a military officer

124
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,460
and meet them.

125
00:06:15,710 --> 00:06:16,640
Don't give away

126
00:06:16,640 --> 00:06:17,480
His Lordship's identity.

127
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:18,520
But...

128
00:06:18,710 --> 00:06:20,030
Why is it happening so suddenly?

129
00:06:20,030 --> 00:06:21,460
Cut it out now.

130
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:23,410
If Ms. Liu insists on seeing His Lordship,

131
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:24,930
tell her he is still at the military camp.

132
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:26,440
Quickly. Go, go, go!

133
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:27,280
Alright, alright.

134
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:32,050
They're here!

135
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:34,080
Send the owner of Yushao Porcelain Shop in.

136
00:06:34,080 --> 00:06:35,500
It's not the owner of Yushao Porcelain Shop.

137
00:06:35,500 --> 00:06:36,780
It's the members of the trade guild.

138
00:06:36,780 --> 00:06:38,520
They're on their knees at the door
to make a petition.

139
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:40,410
His Lordship and Ms. Liu are here.

140
00:06:40,910 --> 00:06:42,170
Won't that give it away?

141
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:46,340
The 12 trade guild members

142
00:06:46,590 --> 00:06:48,660
are asking Lord Huaiyang

143
00:06:49,350 --> 00:06:51,910
to address the Yushao Porcelain Shop's
illegal land acquisition.

144
00:06:51,910 --> 00:06:57,520
- Please rule and judge fairly, Your Lordship.
- Please rule and judge fairly, Your Lordship.

145
00:06:57,520 --> 00:06:58,660
Honey, did you hear that?

146
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,390
These merchants are making

147
00:07:00,390 --> 00:07:01,700
nasty accusations right here.

148
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:02,960
Can't hear it clearly.

149
00:07:03,470 --> 00:07:04,370
Then come here.

150
00:07:04,760 --> 00:07:05,780
- Look at them.
- I...

151
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:07,220
Come and see for yourself.

152
00:07:11,830 --> 00:07:12,700
I saw it. I saw it.

153
00:07:16,270 --> 00:07:17,410
They won't succeed.

154
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:23,520
General Huang.

155
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:24,700
There he is.

156
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,220
Look. There he is.

157
00:07:26,350 --> 00:07:27,530
But that's not His Lordship.

158
00:07:28,390 --> 00:07:30,000
Crowding in front of His Lordship's residence,

159
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:30,840
how disgraceful!

160
00:07:31,030 --> 00:07:31,900
Stand up!

161
00:07:33,790 --> 00:07:36,260
We didn't mean to disturb His Lordship,

162
00:07:36,640 --> 00:07:37,760
but Mrs. Cui

163
00:07:37,760 --> 00:07:39,600
has been unfair in business

164
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:41,530
and illegally seized land.

165
00:07:41,960 --> 00:07:43,370
If this isn't resolved,

166
00:07:43,960 --> 00:07:45,100
our livelihoods

167
00:07:45,270 --> 00:07:47,470
will be at risk.

168
00:07:47,470 --> 00:07:48,620
Yes.

169
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:50,410
If I don't sell my stock soon,

170
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:52,260
my shop will go under.

171
00:07:52,470 --> 00:07:54,410
(The Mansion of Lord Huaiyang)
Please rule and judge fairly.

172
00:07:54,710 --> 00:07:56,660
Please rule and judge fairly, Your Lordship.

173
00:08:03,760 --> 00:08:04,600
Where are you going?

174
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:08,220
Coachman, let's go back.

175
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:14,200
We're not seeing His Lordship?

176
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:17,140
With them causing a scene,

177
00:08:17,350 --> 00:08:19,320
we'd better get out of here.

178
00:08:19,320 --> 00:08:20,160
Exactly.

179
00:08:21,080 --> 00:08:22,370
Besides,

180
00:08:22,910 --> 00:08:25,020
they might not be targeting me.

181
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:26,400
What do you mean?

182
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:28,900
They might be targeting Lord Huaiyang.

183
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:31,840
Where is His Lordship?

184
00:08:31,990 --> 00:08:33,060
Their carriage has left.

185
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,250
It's ridiculous.

186
00:08:34,750 --> 00:08:35,750
This is a joint petition

187
00:08:35,750 --> 00:08:36,820
from 12 trade guild members.

188
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:38,300
Please give it to His Lordship.

189
00:08:38,460 --> 00:08:42,500
(Petition)

190
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:44,510
(Please favor the guild's annual tax)
Merchants only see profit

191
00:08:44,510 --> 00:08:46,400
(and offer more benefits.)
in everything they do.

192
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:47,340
If His Lordship punishes me,

193
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,230
the Zhenzhou authority will

194
00:08:49,230 --> 00:08:50,630
have to change its policies.

195
00:08:50,630 --> 00:08:51,710
That will upset the people.

196
00:08:51,710 --> 00:08:52,770
If he doesn't punish me,

197
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:53,870
those merchants

198
00:08:53,870 --> 00:08:55,120
will definitely make

199
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:55,970
unreasonable demands.

200
00:08:57,280 --> 00:08:59,010
That's not our problem

201
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:00,610
but Lord Huaiyang's.

202
00:09:03,400 --> 00:09:04,420
Honey, is there a problem?

203
00:09:04,590 --> 00:09:05,490
Are you not feeling well?

204
00:09:08,800 --> 00:09:09,730
Just now,

205
00:09:10,350 --> 00:09:11,190
I bumped into something.

206
00:09:11,470 --> 00:09:12,460
It was too bumpy.

207
00:09:18,830 --> 00:09:19,670
Dear,

208
00:09:20,280 --> 00:09:21,610
that's Lord Huaiyang we are talking about.

209
00:09:22,350 --> 00:09:24,770
Even if those members overstep,

210
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:27,820
His Lordship just needs to be a bit firm,

211
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:29,100
and they'll back off.

212
00:09:32,710 --> 00:09:35,700
If Lord Huaiyang really
resorts to rough measures...

213
00:09:38,110 --> 00:09:38,970
If I were him,

214
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:40,580
I wouldn't do that.

215
00:09:41,630 --> 00:09:42,850
Do you have any good ideas?

216
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,280
Great.

217
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:49,400
Great.

218
00:09:50,680 --> 00:09:52,990
The colors are applied well,
the brushstrokes are strong,

219
00:09:52,990 --> 00:09:54,110
and the composition is exquisite.

220
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:56,460
What a magnificent
"Snowy Evening on the Broad Road".

221
00:09:57,110 --> 00:09:57,950
I'll take it.

222
00:10:00,280 --> 00:10:01,120
Mr. Jia.

223
00:10:01,400 --> 00:10:03,420
This painting has been sold.

224
00:10:03,800 --> 00:10:04,640
Sold...

225
00:10:05,110 --> 00:10:06,180
Sold?

226
00:10:06,510 --> 00:10:07,350
To whom?

227
00:10:07,590 --> 00:10:08,430
Well...

228
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,400
I made sure to come

229
00:10:10,400 --> 00:10:12,100
on the agreed day.

230
00:10:12,830 --> 00:10:13,680
The buyer

231
00:10:13,680 --> 00:10:15,700
arrived as soon as the market opened

232
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:18,610
and offered this price.

233
00:10:18,990 --> 00:10:21,250
She'll pick it up after it's mounted.

234
00:10:21,590 --> 00:10:22,430
You know,

235
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:24,540
I thought it was fate.

236
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,060
Fate?

237
00:10:29,110 --> 00:10:30,650
What's fate worth?

238
00:10:31,350 --> 00:10:32,370
She offered this price.

239
00:10:32,830 --> 00:10:33,890
I'll offer this price.

240
00:10:34,350 --> 00:10:35,190
So, this painting

241
00:10:35,800 --> 00:10:36,640
is mine.

242
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:42,460
I can see you really like this painting,

243
00:10:43,280 --> 00:10:44,320
but I can't just back out

244
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:45,890
and tell the buyer that

245
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:47,580
the highest bid won it.

246
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:52,120
How about this?

247
00:10:52,800 --> 00:10:53,750
The buyer seems like

248
00:10:53,750 --> 00:10:54,700
a reasonable lady.

249
00:10:55,160 --> 00:10:56,300
I'll introduce you to her.

250
00:10:56,630 --> 00:10:57,680
And you two

251
00:10:57,680 --> 00:10:58,840
can have tea and a nice chat

252
00:10:58,840 --> 00:11:00,010
at the Zuixian Tavern.

253
00:11:00,750 --> 00:11:01,650
This will be your treat.

254
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:04,850
See if she'll let you have the painting.

255
00:11:07,280 --> 00:11:08,120
Alright.

256
00:11:08,400 --> 00:11:09,240
Then,

257
00:11:09,510 --> 00:11:10,970
everyone will look good.

258
00:11:11,870 --> 00:11:12,710
Yes. Yes.

259
00:11:15,160 --> 00:11:16,200
Hi, Mrs. Xue.

260
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,940
I've been waiting for you.

261
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,510
Whenever your shop gets new fabrics,

262
00:11:20,510 --> 00:11:21,910
I'm always the first to buy them.

263
00:11:21,910 --> 00:11:23,320
- Yes. Exactly.
- Tell me.

264
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:24,770
What fabric do you have today?

265
00:11:25,230 --> 00:11:26,560
Rain silk brocade from Xizhou.

266
00:11:26,560 --> 00:11:28,280
The weave is as delicate as rain threads,

267
00:11:28,280 --> 00:11:29,830
perfect for jackets.

268
00:11:29,830 --> 00:11:31,730
And we only have one bolt.

269
00:11:33,590 --> 00:11:35,480
So it's better than

270
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:36,460
Liu's watered gauze?

271
00:11:37,350 --> 00:11:38,650
I'll take the rain silk brocade.

272
00:11:40,510 --> 00:11:41,560
Mrs. Xue,

273
00:11:41,560 --> 00:11:42,490
what a coincidence.

274
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:45,460
I'm here first.

275
00:11:46,870 --> 00:11:48,320
If that's the case,

276
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:49,700
I won't take what you love.

277
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:53,490
It's not that much.

278
00:11:54,680 --> 00:11:56,710
Mrs. Cui,
since you didn't join the trade guild,

279
00:11:56,710 --> 00:11:58,100
how's your business doing lately?

280
00:11:58,400 --> 00:12:00,060
You've hit the nail on the head.

281
00:12:00,230 --> 00:12:03,010
Someone invited me for business

282
00:12:03,280 --> 00:12:06,460
and reserved the best private room
at Zuixian Tavern for the morning.

283
00:12:09,510 --> 00:12:10,350
Right.

284
00:12:10,590 --> 00:12:11,890
I heard

285
00:12:12,110 --> 00:12:13,750
members of the trade guild

286
00:12:13,750 --> 00:12:14,920
haven't been eating

