- Look at the color.

628
00:26:46,880 --> 00:26:47,890
So exquisite!

629
00:26:48,400 --> 00:26:49,240
Yes.

630
00:26:49,440 --> 00:26:50,550
This is high-quality porcelain.

631
00:26:50,550 --> 00:26:51,980
Yes, it's top quality.

632
00:26:53,600 --> 00:26:54,480
Such craftsmanship

633
00:26:54,480 --> 00:26:55,820
