652
00:27:49,960 --> 00:27:51,980
If you want to meet with the guild members,

653
00:27:52,270 --> 00:27:53,160
Ms. Liu will...

654
00:27:53,160 --> 00:27:54,980
You keep addressing her Ms. Liu.

655
00:27:56,200 --> 00:27:57,930
She's very meticulous.

656
00:27:58,360 --> 00:27:59,400
If one day, you say

657
00:27:59,400 --> 00:28:01,340
