671
00:28:53,030 --> 00:28:54,170
Okay.

672
00:28:57,880 --> 00:28:58,850
How does it taste?

673
00:29:01,230 --> 00:29:02,540
It's a treat for the eyes and the taste buds.

674
00:29:08,680 --> 00:29:09,520
Honey,

675
00:29:09,640 --> 00:29:11,340
