676
00:29:11,510 --> 00:29:12,350
Okay.

677
00:29:13,750 --> 00:29:14,890
Today, let's write

678
00:29:15,120 --> 00:29:16,060
"a strategic planning".

679
00:29:17,310 --> 00:29:18,410
I'll go get the brush and ink.

680
00:29:25,680 --> 00:29:26,540
Liu!

681
00:29:26,920 --> 00:29:28,100
Come out here!

682
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:29,740
Liu!

683
00:29:29,960 --> 00:29:30,800
Come out!

684
00:29:33,790 --> 00:29:34,630
Liu!

685
00:29:35,070 --> 00:29:36,300
Come out!

686
00:29:36,960 --> 00:29:37,800
Nanny Li.

687
00:29:39,120 --> 00:29:41,240
Liu Miantang! You played dirty!

688
00:29:41,240 --> 00:29:42,580
- Who's that?
- Master.

689
00:29:42,750 --> 00:29:44,130
- It's Young Mr. He.
- Own up to it!

690
00:29:44,400 --> 00:29:45,740
- He's up to no good.
- Now you're a coward, huh?

691
00:29:45,990 --> 00:29:46,830
Open the door.

692
00:29:47,260 --> 00:29:50,940
(Cui Mansion)

693
00:29:50,960 --> 00:29:52,020
Come out!

694
00:29:58,070 --> 00:29:58,910
You must be

695
00:29:59,600 --> 00:30:01,340
