696
00:30:01,680 --> 00:30:02,610
I'm Cui Jiu.

697
00:30:03,310 --> 00:30:04,150
What do you want?

698
00:30:04,600 --> 00:30:05,500
You really

699
00:30:05,880 --> 00:30:07,060
have a big heart.

700
00:30:08,920 --> 00:30:09,830
A woman

701
00:30:09,830 --> 00:30:11,840
