702
00:30:11,840 --> 00:30:13,130
Now she is out in the public eye every day.

703
00:30:13,310 --> 00:30:14,500
Are you totally fine with that?

704
00:30:14,640 --> 00:30:16,130
I trust my wife.

705
00:30:20,200 --> 00:30:22,450
I heard you are a Go player.

706
00:30:23,400 --> 00:30:25,720
You must be seeing things

707
00:30:25,720 --> 00:30:27,340
through rose-colored glasses.

708
00:30:28,360 --> 00:30:29,200
After all,

709
00:30:30,120 --> 00:30:31,690
you don't have much experience.

710
00:30:32,680 --> 00:30:33,640
Do you know

711
00:30:33,640 --> 00:30:35,270
who your wife deals with every day?

712
00:30:35,270 --> 00:30:37,480
And do you know what she did to secure

713
00:30:37,480 --> 00:30:38,780
that prime piece of land?

714
00:30:39,120 --> 00:30:40,450
She deals with

715
00:30:40,680 --> 00:30:42,470
the dirty trade guild.

716
00:30:42,470 --> 00:30:44,060
She's come this far

717
00:30:44,270 --> 00:30:46,790
through her own vision and determination.

718
00:30:46,790 --> 00:30:47,850
Her vision?

719
00:30:48,360 --> 00:30:49,370
Ridiculous.

720
00:30:49,680 --> 00:30:51,120
We, the trade guild members,

721
00:30:51,120 --> 00:30:52,120
couldn't get it done.

722
00:30:52,120 --> 00:30:53,720
She's just a young woman,

723
00:30:53,720 --> 00:30:54,880
and she managed to do it?

724
00:30:54,880 --> 00:30:56,070
But this young lady

725
00:30:56,070 --> 00:30:58,340
is more capable than all you men.

726
00:31:02,880 --> 00:31:04,160
I'm not wasting my breath with you.

727
00:31:04,160 --> 00:31:05,270
Bring Liu out here.

728
00:31:05,270 --> 00:31:06,450
I need to ask her something.

729
00:31:08,310 --> 00:31:09,360
What are you doing?

730
00:31:09,360 --> 00:31:10,450
Let me go!

731
00:31:11,270 --> 00:31:14,130
If you dare speak ill of my wife again,

732
00:31:14,680 --> 00:31:15,820
you might

733
00:31:16,160 --> 00:31:17,580
lose that arm.

734
00:31:19,840 --> 00:31:21,340
Fine, you...

735
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:25,100
You listen to everything that woman says, huh?

736
00:31:25,640 --> 00:31:27,170
You're not much of a man!

737
00:31:28,120 --> 00:31:29,340
You... I...

738
00:31:37,120 --> 00:31:39,020
My husband is righteous and kind.

739
00:31:39,160 --> 00:31:40,020
He supports his family.

740
00:31:40,680 --> 00:31:42,030
Unlike you, who fails

741
00:31:42,030 --> 00:31:42,930
at everything,

742
00:31:43,230 --> 00:31:44,440
and is only capable of bullying

743
00:31:44,440 --> 00:31:46,260
the weak and women,

744
00:31:46,550 --> 00:31:48,300
he's a real standup man.

745
00:31:52,880 --> 00:31:53,720
Alright.

746
00:31:54,160 --> 00:31:55,000
You...

747
00:31:55,880 --> 00:31:56,720
Wait for it.

748
00:31:56,880 --> 00:31:57,890
Just you wait!

749
00:32:00,420 --> 00:32:03,380
(Cui Mansion)

750
00:32:06,200 --> 00:32:07,040
Clear out!

751
00:32:09,450 --> 00:32:10,690
- He escaped.
- Nanny Li.

752
00:32:12,310 --> 00:32:13,370
Wipe the door.

753
00:32:16,960 --> 00:32:18,160
Stop looking.

754
00:32:18,160 --> 00:32:19,130
Go away.

755
00:32:19,440 --> 00:32:20,280
You're good.

756
00:32:23,900 --> 00:32:26,660
(Tea)

757
00:32:26,660 --> 00:32:28,050
Take a look!

758
00:32:28,510 --> 00:32:29,990
It's so fresh. Have a look.

759
00:32:30,920 --> 00:32:32,830
(Cold Rain Courtyard)
Give me some of that.

760
00:32:33,600 --> 00:32:34,880
- Okay, that's enough.
- Here you are.

761
00:32:35,560 --> 00:32:36,400
Thank you.

762
00:32:48,270 --> 00:32:49,110
Young Master.

763
00:32:49,740 --> 00:32:55,860
(Cold Rain Courtyard)

764
00:32:56,070 --> 00:32:56,910
Young Master?

765
00:33:00,840 --> 00:33:01,690
You're back.

766
00:33:04,840 --> 00:33:05,680
Young Master.

767
00:33:06,600 --> 00:33:08,850
I sent Zhou Cuo to Lingquan Town
to pick someone up.

768
00:33:09,070 --> 00:33:10,310
Yet, under my name,

769
00:33:10,310 --> 00:33:11,510
you sent him halfway north

770
00:33:11,510 --> 00:33:12,850
and went to Zhenzhou yourself

771
00:33:14,310 --> 00:33:15,930
without bringing her back.

772
00:33:16,880 --> 00:33:18,600
Sorry, I took matters into my own hands.

773
00:33:18,600 --> 00:33:19,440
Why?

774
00:33:19,600 --> 00:33:20,990
Ms. Liu left Mount Yang

775
00:33:20,990 --> 00:33:22,410
in a huff with me,

776
00:33:22,600 --> 00:33:23,500
so

777
00:33:23,750 --> 00:33:25,820
I wanted to explain things to her in person.

778
00:33:26,360 --> 00:33:27,200
Moreover,

779
00:33:28,360 --> 00:33:30,890
I feared that might trouble you.

780
00:33:31,990 --> 00:33:35,020
So I went alone without informing you.

781
00:33:36,200 --> 00:33:37,690
How is she now?

782
00:33:38,510 --> 00:33:39,610
Ms. Liu

783
00:33:39,920 --> 00:33:41,540
found her true love

784
00:33:42,750 --> 00:33:45,340
and married an ordinary merchant.

785
00:33:46,710 --> 00:33:48,230
When she saw me that day,

786
00:33:48,230 --> 00:33:50,160
she didn't want to say a single word.

787
00:33:50,160 --> 00:33:51,130
She turned and walked away.

788
00:33:51,920 --> 00:33:52,760
So I think

789
00:33:53,600 --> 00:33:55,370
she still holds a grudge against us,

790
00:33:56,200 --> 00:33:57,600
wanting to sever all ties

791
00:33:57,600 --> 00:33:58,580
with Mount Yang.

792
00:33:58,750 --> 00:34:00,210
Sever all ties?

793
00:34:06,600 --> 00:34:08,170
Could she really let go?

794
00:34:11,070 --> 00:34:12,170
What are you going to do?

795
00:34:16,960 --> 00:34:17,860
Since she won't come to me,

796
00:34:19,400 --> 00:34:20,330
I'll go to her

797
00:34:22,510 --> 00:34:24,210
and explain everything.

798
00:34:24,800 --> 00:34:25,640
No.

799
00:34:26,510 --> 00:34:28,380
Lingquan Town is under Lord Huaiyang's control.

800
00:34:28,630 --> 00:34:29,510
Going there

801
00:34:29,510 --> 00:34:30,810
would be like walking into a trap.

802
00:34:33,670 --> 00:34:34,770
Young Master, don't forget

803
00:34:35,840 --> 00:34:37,900
we have more important things to handle.

804
00:35:06,800 --> 00:35:09,330
Are you making crab roe rice?

805
00:35:09,880 --> 00:35:10,720
Yes.

806
00:35:11,510 --> 00:35:13,170
My mother taught me this.

807
00:35:13,670 --> 00:35:14,510
When I was a child,

808
00:35:14,510 --> 00:35:15,590
she often made this dish

809
00:35:15,590 --> 00:35:16,430
for my father and me.

810
00:35:17,400 --> 00:35:18,540
She said

811
00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:19,920
crab roe rice

812
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:21,360
is best enjoyed

813
00:35:21,360 --> 00:35:22,250
with someone you love.

814
00:35:25,360 --> 00:35:26,630
We've bought

815
00:35:26,630 --> 00:35:28,250
a lot of crabs in the past,

816
00:35:29,280 --> 00:35:31,610
but I don't remember you ever making this.

817
00:35:32,880 --> 00:35:34,730
Why do you suddenly want to make it now?

818
00:35:35,720 --> 00:35:36,730
Are the scallions chopped?

819
00:35:37,990 --> 00:35:39,020
Yes, they're ready.

820
00:35:43,840 --> 00:35:44,680
Here.

821
00:36:51,070 --> 00:36:51,940
What's wrong?

822
00:36:52,880 --> 00:36:53,770
It's not hot.

823
00:36:58,240 --> 00:36:59,190
Soft and glutinous.

824
00:36:59,190 --> 00:37:00,030
Delicious.

825
00:37:07,240 --> 00:37:08,080
Tasty, right?

826
00:37:09,320 --> 00:37:10,250
I'll serve myself.

827
00:37:11,360 --> 00:37:12,360
Why do you need to be coaxed

828
00:37:12,360 --> 00:37:13,500
just to eat

829
00:37:13,630 --> 00:37:14,650
like a child?

830
00:37:23,190 --> 00:37:25,460
Madam, dinner is ready.

831
00:37:26,070 --> 00:37:26,910
Okay.

832
00:37:27,590 --> 00:37:28,580
I'll be right back.

833
00:38:05,920 --> 00:38:06,760
Go ahead, taste it.

834
00:38:12,880 --> 00:38:13,720
How is it?

835
00:38:16,990 --> 00:38:18,480
Even more delicious

836
00:38:18,480 --> 00:38:19,540
than the usual June yellow crabs.

837
00:38:20,840 --> 00:38:23,400
I simmered the male crab's roe
to make crab fat,

838
00:38:23,400 --> 00:38:24,940
and stir-fried the female crab's roe.

839
00:38:25,320 --> 00:38:26,960
I used black pig lard for flavor

840
00:38:26,960 --> 00:38:28,470
and mixed it with steaming hot rice.

841
00:38:28,470 --> 00:38:29,470
The hotter, the better.

842
00:38:29,470 --> 00:38:31,290
That's how to bring out the original taste.

843
00:38:33,190 --> 00:38:34,030
Exactly.

844
00:38:41,510 --> 00:38:43,670
Madam, even with your old injury,

845
00:38:43,670 --> 00:38:45,980
you insisted on picking out
the crab roe yourself.

846
00:38:46,880 --> 00:38:48,190
Next time,

847
00:38:48,190 --> 00:38:49,980
just ask me to do it.

848
00:38:50,360 --> 00:38:51,250
It's okay.

849
00:39:15,510 --> 00:39:16,350
Is it hurt?

850
00:39:22,670 --> 00:39:23,770
The rice will get cold.

851
00:39:23,880 --> 00:39:25,020
It took me so long to make it.

852
00:39:25,440 --> 00:39:26,280
My arms are sore.

853
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:37,250
Who's that at this late hour?

854
00:39:38,110 --> 00:39:39,020
Coming.

855
00:39:39,670 --> 00:39:40,610
Who is it?

856
00:39:40,840 --> 00:39:41,810
It's me,

857
00:39:42,320 --> 00:39:43,330
Physician Zhao.

858
00:39:43,630 --> 00:39:44,470
Today,

859
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:46,500
I bought some crabs

860
00:39:47,240 --> 00:39:49,500
and stopped by

861
00:39:49,840 --> 00:39:52,460
to let Ms. Liu have a taste.

862
00:39:52,920 --> 00:39:54,880
I-I didn't know why

863
00:39:54,880 --> 00:39:56,460
Physician Zhao would bring crabs today.

864
00:39:58,030 --> 00:39:59,020
I invited him.

865
00:40:00,280 --> 00:40:01,650
It's better to save trouble.

866
00:40:02,070 --> 00:40:03,760
Honey, you go meet Physician Zhao.

867
00:40:03,760 --> 00:40:04,730
I'll go to the backyard.

868
00:40:04,840 --> 00:40:05,680
Okay.

869
00:40:23,360 --> 00:40:24,200
Master.

870
00:40:33,400 --> 00:40:34,240
Where is she?

871
00:40:36,880 --> 00:40:37,720
Who?

872
00:40:38,280 --> 00:40:39,120
Well,

873
00:40:39,400 --> 00:40:40,360
where's Ms. Liu?

874
00:40:40,360 --> 00:40:41,540
Why do you care?

875
00:40:46,440 --> 00:40:48,170
Do you even know where your true home is?

876
00:40:50,320 --> 00:40:51,610
Cousin Lian asked me to bring this to you.

877
00:40:53,590 --> 00:40:55,190
Good for her for finding you.

878
00:40:55,190 --> 00:40:56,380
Although she didn't say anything,

879
00:40:56,630 --> 00:40:58,470
I could see in her eyes that she was thinking,

880
00:40:58,470 --> 00:40:59,990
"You, Zhao Quan, are no good.

881
00:40:59,990 --> 00:41:01,210
All men are the same."

882
00:41:09,880 --> 00:41:10,720
Give it to me.

883
00:41:12,360 --> 00:41:13,330
So delicious!

884
00:41:13,840 --> 00:41:15,210
This wasn't made by Nanny Li, was it?

885
00:41:16,240 --> 00:41:17,540
Move your chopsticks away.

886
00:41:22,720 --> 00:41:24,130
W-What do you mean?

887
00:41:25,280 --> 00:41:26,610
It wasn't made for you.

888
00:41:26,960 --> 00:41:27,800
If you want to eat,

889
00:41:28,030 --> 00:41:28,980
go back home.

890
00:41:32,800 --> 00:41:33,860
Are you jealous?

891
00:41:35,150 --> 00:41:36,060
No.

892
00:41:36,320 --> 00:41:37,160
It's mine.

893
00:41:37,720 --> 00:41:39,210
Then why don't you share some with me?

894
00:41:39,720 --> 00:41:40,760
These are for you.

895
00:41:40,760 --> 00:41:41,650
Have as much as you like.

896
00:41:46,470 --> 00:41:48,130
Are you really jealous?

897
00:41:51,400 --> 00:41:52,460
Then it's right.

898
00:41:52,630 --> 00:41:53,810
Right about what? I'm not jealous.

899
00:41:54,320 --> 00:41:55,160
You

900
00:41:55,320 --> 00:41:56,380
are not interested in her,

901
00:41:56,920 --> 00:41:58,510
and in her confusion,

902
00:41:58,510 --> 00:41:59,580
she mistakes you for her husband.

903
00:42:00,150 --> 00:42:02,190
This doesn't even count as

904
00:42:02,190 --> 00:42:03,030
the start of a romance.

905
00:42:03,440 --> 00:42:05,110
What if she meets a man

906
00:42:05,110 --> 00:42:06,240
who truly wins her heart...

907
00:42:06,240 --> 00:42:07,380
That won't be you.

908
00:42:07,720 --> 00:42:08,770
Why not?

909
00:42:09,360 --> 00:42:10,610
I'm so charming.

910
00:42:11,070 --> 00:42:11,910
I can be the one.

911
00:42:12,190 --> 00:42:13,100
Give me a bite.

912
00:42:17,280 --> 00:42:18,120
What are you doing?

913
00:42:18,920 --> 00:42:19,760
Nanny Li,

914
00:42:20,240 --> 00:42:21,080
clear the dishes.

915
00:42:41,920 --> 00:42:43,460
Since Ms. Liu joined the trade guild,

916
00:42:43,590 --> 00:42:46,110
