imperial tribute business.

917
00:42:46,110 --> 00:42:48,020
She's been well-regarded
by the other members.

918
00:42:48,240 --> 00:42:49,550
Business at the Yushao Porcelain Shop

919
00:42:49,550 --> 00:42:50,860
is thriving.

920
00:42:51,720 --> 00:42:53,860
This month,
it brought in over 300 taels of silver.

921
00:42:58,880 --> 00:42:59,720
My Lord?

922
00:43:01,590 --> 00:43:02,430
My Lord?

923
00:43:05,110 --> 00:43:06,670
Yes. She's more interesting

924
00:43:06,670 --> 00:43:08,380
than I initially thought.

925
00:43:09,070 --> 00:43:11,280
Ms. Liu has diligently taken

926
00:43:11,280 --> 00:43:13,100
on the role of hostess for the Cui family.

927
00:43:13,440 --> 00:43:14,580
But what if

928
00:43:14,880 --> 00:43:17,170
she finds out the truth later on...

929
00:43:20,630 --> 00:43:22,460
Please forgive me for being blunt,

930
00:43:22,590 --> 00:43:23,460
My Lord,

931
00:43:24,320 --> 00:43:26,580
