932
00:43:27,920 --> 00:43:29,810
I don't want to trouble her with rules.

933
00:43:29,990 --> 00:43:31,020
So let her be.

934
00:43:31,590 --> 00:43:33,580
Let her

935
00:43:33,880 --> 00:43:35,170
earn enough for her future.

936
00:43:35,990 --> 00:43:37,690
Once I catch Lu Wen,

937
00:43:39,070 --> 00:43:40,130
this playing house game

938
00:43:40,440 --> 00:43:41,580
will be over.

939
00:43:43,920 --> 00:43:46,650
Now I understand, My Lord.

